      <h2>Contribute</h2>

      <p><a href="http://shields.io/">Shields.io</a> is written in Python using
      <a href="http://aspen.io/">Aspen</a> and is in the public domain.</p>

      <p>It wraps a Node.js CLI called <code><a
          href="https://github.com/cainus/shielded">shielded</a></code>.</p>

      <pre>$ git clone git@github.com:gittip/shields.io.git
$ cd shields.io
$ make run</pre>

      <p>Dependencies are included in the <a
        href="https://github.com/gittip/shields.io/tree/master/vendor">vendor</a>
      directory.</p>

      <p>Look at <a
      href="https://github.com/gittip/shields.io/blob/master/shields_io/services.py">shields_io/services.py</a>
      to add a new service.</p>


